# Validation and Definition of Done

A task is complete only when changes are consistent with the SDD and the relevant docs/checks are updated.

## Required checks

- Run `python3 scripts/harness_validate.py` before closing repository-governance tasks.
- Run available tests when the environment provides the needed tooling.
- If a tool is missing, document the missing tool and the command that could not be run.
- Verify key files after scaffold/setup work:
  - `AGENT.md`
  - `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`
  - `docs/specs/SDD.md`
  - `.cursor/rules/*`
  - `docs/prompts/00-master-prompt.md`

## Documentation paths

- Prompt files live in `docs/prompts/`.
- Checklist files live in `docs/checklists/`.
- Template files live in `docs/templates/`.
- SDD entrypoint lives in `docs/specs/SDD.md`.
- Detailed SDD modules live in `docs/sdd/`.
